descriptionHtml:
Sometimes I like to go hunt horkers but I don\'t get much from them. I felt like there tusks should be worth more so this mod gives them a weight of 5 and worth 150. Pretty simple.

Just copy the esp into your data file and then load the esp.

If you want all pelts, hides and tusks to be changed, check out my hunters mod:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7800

If you want to run faster or play with skooma check out my other mods
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7486
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7269
